('Operations','Aviation','Geopolitical airspace closure disrupting routes','Armed conflict; sanctions; bilateral dispute between states','Route cancellation; increased fuel burn on alternate routes; commercial loss','Route risk assessment; airspace monitoring; alternate routing plans; insurance for war risk'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Pandemic or widespread health crisis','Infectious disease outbreak; government-mandated restrictions','Staff unavailability; office closure; supply chain disruption; demand shock','Pandemic response plan; remote working capability; cross-training; supplier resilience'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Cyber incident causing extended operational outage','Ransomware; DDoS; critical system compromise','Inability to serve clients; data loss; regulatory breach; reputational damage','Cyber incident response plan; BCP for manual workarounds; cyber insurance; DR testing'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Natural disaster affecting primary site','Flood; fire; earthquake; severe weather','Facility loss; staff unavailability; equipment damage; data loss','BCP; alternate site; remote working; data backup offsite; insurance'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Telecommunications failure','ISP outage; exchange fire; undersea cable cut','Inability to communicate with clients or staff; operational standstill','Redundant telecoms; mobile failover; satellite backup for critical functions'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Loss of critical third-party service','SaaS platform outage; cloud provider failure; payment processor down','Operational disruption; inability to process transactions; client impact','Dependency mapping; SLA review; manual workaround procedures; multi-vendor'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Simultaneous loss of multiple key personnel','Common event such as travel accident or pandemic; unplanned mass departure','Leadership vacuum; operational disruption; client concern','Succession plans; cross-training; travel policy restricting key people on same flight'),
('BCM','All Sectors','BCP plan not fit for purpose','Plan not tested; not updated after changes; inadequate scope','Extended recovery time; uncoordinated response; exacerbated impact','Annual BCP review; regular testing; lessons learned incorporated'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Failure to meet RTO / RPO targets after incident','Untested DR; inadequate backup frequency; resource constraints during recovery','Extended client impact; SLA breach; regulatory notification obligations','DR testing against RTO/RPO; monitoring; resource pre-positioning'),
('BCM','All Sectors','BCP activation failure - response not invoked promptly','Unclear trigger criteria; decision-making paralysis; poor escalation','Avoidable additional damage; prolonged impact; regulatory concern','Clear activation criteria; defined Crisis Management Team; regular exercises'),
('BCM','All Sectors','Inadequate crisis communications','No communications plan; poor spokesperson training; social media vacuum','Reputational damage; client concern; employee anxiety; regulatory scrutiny','Crisis communications plan; trained spokesperson; holding statements ready'),
('BCM','Oil & Gas (Upstream)','Extended production shutdown following well incident or natural disaster','Well blowout; pipeline rupture; sabotage; seismic event','Revenue loss; supply contract default; government production obligations breached; remediation cost','Emergency response plan; business interruption insurance; backup production assets; force majeure clauses'),
('BCM','Utilities','Cascading infrastructure failure - combined cyber and physical event','Coordinated attack on OT systems and physical infrastructure; extreme weather','Extended nationwide outage; public safety emergency; economic disruption','Multi-hazard scenario planning; hardened infrastructure; government coordination; emergency response plan'),
('Security','All Sectors','Physical security breach - unauthorised site access','Tailgating; visitor management failure; compromised access credentials','Theft of assets; access to sensitive information; safety incident','Access control system; visitor management; security training; CCTV'),
('Security','All Sectors','Theft of assets - laptops, devices, documents','Inadequate physical security; working in public spaces; unsecured storage','Data breach; financial loss; operational disruption','Device encryption; clear desk policy; secure storage; asset tracking'),
('Security','All Sectors','Sensitive document or data disposal failure','Documents not shredded; digital files not securely deleted; inadequate policy','Data breach; regulatory breach; competitive intelligence leakage','Secure shredding service; secure delete tools; disposal policy; training'),
('Security','All Sectors','Workplace violence or threatening behaviour','Disgruntled employee; external aggressor; domestic violence spillover','Staff injury; psychological harm; operational disruption; legal liability','Threat assessment; security protocols; staff training; emergency procedures'),
('Security','All Sectors','Access credential theft or compromise','Phishing; credential stuffing; weak passwords; sharing of credentials','Unauthorized system access; data breach; fraud','MFA; password manager; credential monitoring; phishing awareness training'),
('Security','All Sectors','Security awareness failure - untrained staff','Inadequate training programme; infrequent refreshers; poor engagement','Increased susceptibility to phishing, social engineering, and policy breaches','Annual security awareness training; phishing simulations; microlearning modules'),
('Security','All Sectors','Clean desk / clear screen policy non-compliance','Culture; remote working; inadequate monitoring','Sensitive information visible to unauthorized persons; compliance breach','Policy communication; manager enforcement; periodic walk-through checks'),
('Security','All Sectors','Inadequate offboarding - access not revoked promptly','Manual process; HR/IT coordination failure; no automated deprovisioning','Former employee retaining access; potential data exfiltration or sabotage','Automated offboarding workflow; same-day access revocation; exit checklist'),
('Security','Oil & Gas (Upstream)','Physical attack or sabotage of production infrastructure','Terrorism; civil unrest; disgruntled contractor; state-sponsored attack','Production shutdown; environmental incident; staff casualties; geopolitical escalation','Security risk assessment; perimeter security; security personnel; government liaison; business interruption insurance'),
('Security','Retail','Organised retail crime - coordinated theft or robbery','Criminal gangs; inadequate deterrents; high-value merchandise concentration','Staff safety risk; significant stock loss; store closure; insurance cost impact','CCTV; security personnel; electronic article surveillance; inter-retailer intelligence sharing');
INSERT INTO control_library (name, description, control_type, automation, framework_reference, testing_frequency) VALUES
('Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)','Requires users to verify identity using at least two factors before gaining system access. Dramatically reduces risk of credential-based compromise.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.9.4.2 | SOC 2 CC6.1 | NIST AC-17','Ongoing'),
('Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)','Limits system access based on defined job roles. Users receive only the permissions needed to perform their function.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.9.2 | SOC 2 CC6.3 | NIST AC-2','Quarterly review'),
('Endpoint Protection / Antivirus','Deploys anti-malware software on all endpoints. Prevents, detects, and blocks malicious code including ransomware and trojans.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.12.2.1 | SOC 2 CC6.8 | NIST SI-3','Continuous'),
('Email Filtering and Anti-Phishing','Filters inbound email for malicious links, attachments, and spoofed senders. Quarantines suspicious messages before delivery.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.12.2 | SOC 2 CC6.8 | NIST SI-8','Continuous'),
('Network Firewall and Segmentation','Controls traffic entering and leaving the network. Segments internal networks to limit lateral movement in event of a breach.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.13.1 | SOC 2 CC6.6 | NIST SC-7','Continuous'),
('Data Encryption at Rest','Encrypts stored data so it is unreadable if storage media is lost or stolen. Applied to databases, file systems, and removable media.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.10.1 | SOC 2 CC6.1 | NIST SC-28','Continuous'),
('Data Encryption in Transit','Encrypts data as it moves across networks using TLS/HTTPS. Prevents interception of data in transit.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.13.2.3 | SOC 2 CC6.7 | NIST SC-8','Continuous'),
('Patch Management','Ensures all operating systems, applications, and firmware are updated promptly with security patches. Closes known vulnerabilities before exploitation.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.12.6.1 | SOC 2 CC7.1 | NIST SI-2','Monthly'),
('Vulnerability Scanning','Automated scanning of systems and applications for known vulnerabilities. Results prioritised and tracked through to remediation.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.12.6.1 | SOC 2 CC7.1 | NIST RA-5','Monthly'),
('Penetration Testing','Authorised simulated attack on systems to identify exploitable vulnerabilities. Conducted by qualified testers.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.14.2.8 | SOC 2 CC4.1 | NIST CA-8','Annual'),
('Security Awareness Training','Annual programme educating all staff on phishing, social engineering, clean desk, and acceptable use. Includes mandatory completion tracking.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.7.2.2 | SOC 2 CC1.4 | NIST AT-2','Annual'),
('Phishing Simulation','Simulated phishing emails sent to staff to test susceptibility. Those who click receive immediate targeted training.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.7.2.2 | SOC 2 CC2.2 | NIST AT-2','Quarterly'),
('Password Policy Enforcement','Technical controls enforce minimum password length, complexity, history, and expiry. Prevents use of weak or reused passwords.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.9.4.3 | SOC 2 CC6.1 | NIST IA-5','Continuous'),
('Mobile Device Management (MDM)','Centrally manages and secures mobile devices. Enforces encryption, screen lock, and enables remote wipe if a device is lost.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.6.2.1 | SOC 2 CC6.1 | NIST MP-5','Continuous'),
('Secure SDLC','Integrates security requirements, code review, and security testing into all stages of software development.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.14.2 | SOC 2 CC8.1 | NIST SA-15','Per release'),
('Software Composition Analysis (SCA)','Automated scanning of open-source libraries for known vulnerabilities (CVEs). Alerts developers before vulnerable packages are deployed.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.14.2.1 | SOC 2 CC7.1 | NIST SA-12','Per build'),
('Third-Party / Supplier Due Diligence','Assesses suppliers'' security, financial health, and compliance posture before onboarding. Risk-tiered based on criticality.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.15.1 | SOC 2 CC9.2 | NIST SR-3','At onboarding + annual'),
('Segregation of Duties','Ensures no single individual can complete a high-risk transaction end-to-end. Reduces fraud and error risk.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.6.1.2 | SOC 2 CC5.2 | NIST AC-5','Ongoing'),
('Dual Authorisation for Payments','Requires two independent approvers for payments above defined thresholds. Prevents unauthorised or fraudulent payment initiation.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.6.1.2 | SOC 2 CC5.2','Continuous'),
('Data Loss Prevention (DLP)','Monitors and controls movement of sensitive data to prevent unauthorised transfer via email, USB, or cloud upload.','Preventive','Automated','ISO 27001 A.13.2 | SOC 2 CC6.7 | NIST MP-7','Continuous'),
('IT Change Management Process','All production changes documented, tested, and approved via Change Advisory Board before deployment. Includes rollback plan.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.12.1.2 | SOC 2 CC8.1 | NIST CM-3','Per change'),
('Physical Access Control','Badge-based access restricts entry to offices and data centres to authorised personnel. Access logs maintained.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.11.1 | SOC 2 CC6.4 | NIST PE-3','Continuous'),
('Visitor Management','All visitors signed in; identity verified; escorted while on premises. Visitor log maintained.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.11.1.2 | SOC 2 CC6.4 | NIST PE-8','Continuous'),
('Pre-Employment Background Screening','Screening of candidates for relevant roles: identity, criminal history, reference checks, credential verification.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.7.1.1 | SOC 2 CC1.1 | NIST PS-3','At hire'),
('Business Continuity Planning','Documented BCP covering critical processes, recovery procedures, and communication plans. Maintained, tested, and board-approved.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 A1.2 | NIST CP-2','Annual review + test'),
('Succession Planning','Identifies successors for all critical roles. Development plans in place to ready successors. Board-reviewed annually.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.7.1 | SOC 2 CC1.1','Annual'),
('Insurance Programme','Maintains appropriate coverage: cyber liability, professional indemnity, public liability, business interruption, D&O.','Preventive','Manual','SOC 2 A1.1 | ISO 22301','Annual review'),
('Anti-Bribery and Corruption Policy and Training','Policy prohibiting bribery, with training for all staff. Includes gifts register and third-party due diligence requirements.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 37001 | SOC 2 CC1.3','Annual'),
('Acceptable Use Policy','Defines permitted and prohibited use of company systems, devices, and data. All staff must acknowledge annually.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.8.1.3 | SOC 2 CC1.3','Annual'),
('Clear Desk and Clear Screen Policy','Requires employees to secure sensitive documents and lock screens when away from desks.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.11.2.9 | SOC 2 CC6.1','Ongoing'),
('Permit to Work (PTW) System','Formal authorisation process for hazardous work (confined space, hot work, working at height, energy isolation). Ensures hazards are controlled before work starts.','Preventive','Manual','ISO 45001 | OSHA | Local HSE regulations','Per activity'),
('Process Hazard Analysis (PHA / HAZOP)','Systematic examination of processes to identify and evaluate hazards. Results in documented risk register and safeguard requirements for process plant.','Preventive','Manual','IEC 61511 | API RP 14C | ISO 45001','At design + periodic revalidation'),
('OT / SCADA Network Segmentation and Security','Segregates operational technology networks from IT networks using firewalls and DMZs. Restricts remote access. OT-specific vulnerability management applied.','Preventive','Semi-automated','IEC 62443 | NIST SP 800-82 | ISO 27001','Continuous'),
('Asset Integrity Management Programme','Systematic inspection, testing, and maintenance of safety-critical equipment to ensure fitness for service. Covers pressure vessels, pipelines, and rotating equipment.','Preventive','Semi-automated','API 510/570/653 | ISO 55001 | ASME','Per asset schedule'),
('Fatigue Risk Management System (FRMS)','Defines maximum duty hours, minimum rest periods, and handover requirements for safety-critical roles. Includes fit-for-duty assessments.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ICAO Doc 9966 | CAR | Local labour law','Continuous'),
('Environmental Management System (ISO 14001)','Systematic approach to identifying, managing, and reducing environmental impacts. Includes permit compliance register, monitoring, and incident reporting.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 14001:2015 | Local environmental regulations','Continuous'),
('Food Safety Management System (HACCP / ISO 22000)','Identifies critical control points in food handling and implements controls to prevent contamination. Includes supplier certification and temperature monitoring.','Preventive','Semi-automated','HACCP | ISO 22000 | Local food authority regulations','Continuous'),
('Sanctions Screening and Trade Compliance Programme','Screens customers, suppliers, and transactions against sanctions lists (OFAC, EU, UN). Includes trade compliance officer, procedures, and regular training.','Preventive','Automated','OFAC | UN Security Council Resolutions | EU sanctions | Local regulations','Continuous'),
('Sharia Product Pre-Approval Process','All new Islamic finance products reviewed and approved by Sharia Supervisory Board (SSB) before launch. Includes product documentation review and fatwa issuance.','Preventive','Manual','AAOIFI | Local Central Bank Islamic finance regulations | IFSB','Per new product'),
('Migrant Worker Welfare Programme','Ensures migrant workers receive fair wages, safe accommodation, and access to grievance mechanisms. Aligned to ILO standards and local Ministry of Labour requirements.','Preventive','Manual','ILO conventions | UAE/KSA/Qatar Labour Law | GCC migrant worker standards','Ongoing'),
('Fleet Safety Management Programme','Covers driver vetting, licence verification, mandatory safety training, vehicle maintenance schedules, telematics, and journey management for high-risk routes.','Preventive','Semi-automated','ISO 39001 | Local transport regulations','Continuous'),
('Commodity / Price Risk Hedging Policy','Defines approved hedging instruments, exposure limits, hedge ratios, and counterparty requirements for commodity and FX risk. Reviewed by risk committee.','Preventive','Manual','IFRS 9 | Local regulatory requirements','Quarterly review'),
('Security Event Monitoring / SIEM','Aggregates and correlates security events from across systems. Alerts on anomalous activity. Supports forensic investigation.','Detective','Automated','ISO 27001 A.12.4 | SOC 2 CC7.2 | NIST SI-4','Continuous'),
('Audit Log Review','Regular review of system and application audit logs to detect unauthorised access, changes, or anomalous behaviour.','Detective','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.12.4.1 | SOC 2 CC7.2 | NIST AU-6','Monthly'),
('User Access Review / Recertification','Periodic manager review of team members'' access rights. Removes stale or excessive access. Supports least-privilege.','Detective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.9.2.5 | SOC 2 CC6.3 | NIST AC-2','Quarterly'),
('Internal Audit Programme','Risk-based programme of independent assurance reviews covering controls, compliance, and operational processes. Reports to audit committee.','Detective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.18.2 | SOC 2 CC4.1 | NIST CA-7','Annual programme'),
('Financial Reconciliation','Regular reconciliation of key financial accounts (bank, AR, AP, payroll) to detect errors, omissions, or fraudulent transactions.','Detective','Semi-automated','SOC 2 CC5.2 | NIST AU-3','Monthly'),
('KRI Monitoring and Reporting','Key Risk Indicators tracked against thresholds. Amber/red breaches trigger management escalation and risk owner response.','Detective','Semi-automated','ISO 31000 | SOC 2 CC4.1','Monthly'),
('Supplier Performance Review','Structured review of critical suppliers against SLA and KPI targets. Identifies early warning signs of performance deterioration.','Detective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.15.2 | SOC 2 CC9.2','Quarterly'),
('Health and Safety Inspection','Periodic workplace safety inspections to identify hazards, near misses, and non-compliance. Findings tracked to closure.','Detective','Manual','ISO 45001 | WHS legislation','Monthly'),
('Regulatory Change Monitoring','Horizon scanning for upcoming regulatory changes. Assessed for impact and response plan developed.','Detective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.18.1 | SOC 2 CC1.2','Monthly'),
('Management Accounts Review','Monthly review of management accounts against budget by senior management. Variances investigated and explained.','Detective','Manual','SOC 2 CC5.2','Monthly'),
('Data Quality Monitoring','Automated checks on data completeness, accuracy, and consistency. Anomalies flagged for investigation.','Detective','Automated','SOC 2 CC5.2 | NIST AU-3','Continuous'),
('Whistleblower / Speak-Up Hotline','Anonymous reporting channel for staff to raise concerns about misconduct, fraud, or ethical violations without fear of retaliation.','Detective','Semi-automated','ISO 37001 | SOC 2 CC1.5','Continuous'),
('User Behaviour Analytics (UBA)','Automated detection of unusual user behaviour: login times, data access volumes, unusual download patterns. Alerts security team.','Detective','Automated','ISO 27001 A.12.4 | SOC 2 CC7.2 | NIST SI-4','Continuous'),
('IT Asset Inventory and Review','Maintains accurate register of all hardware, software, and cloud assets. Regular reconciliation to identify shadow IT and unmanaged devices.','Detective','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.8 | SOC 2 CC6.1 | NIST CM-8','Quarterly'),
('Contract Obligations Monitoring','Tracks key contract dates, obligations, and SLA metrics. Alerts owners of upcoming deadlines or breaches.','Detective','Semi-automated','SOC 2 CC9.2','Monthly'),
('Customer Satisfaction / NPS Monitoring','Regular measurement of client satisfaction (CSAT, NPS). Negative trends escalated to account management.','Detective','Semi-automated','SOC 2 CC2.3','Quarterly'),
('BCP Currency Review','Regular check that BCP documentation is current: contact lists, system names, recovery procedures. Updated after any material change.','Detective','Manual','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 A1.2','Semi-annual'),
('Payroll Variance Analysis','Monthly comparison of payroll totals against prior period and budget. Investigates unexpected movements before payment.','Detective','Manual','SOC 2 CC5.2','Monthly'),
('Network Traffic Analysis','Monitors network traffic for unusual patterns suggesting intrusion, data exfiltration, or C2 communication.','Detective','Automated','ISO 27001 A.12.4 | SOC 2 CC7.2 | NIST SI-4','Continuous'),
('Backup Verification and Restore Testing','Automated verification that backup jobs complete successfully. Periodic restore tests to confirm data can be recovered within RTO/RPO.','Detective','Semi-automated','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 A1.2 | NIST CP-9','Monthly verify; quarterly restore test'),
('Project Milestone and Budget Tracking','Structured tracking of project milestones, costs, and risks. RAG status reported to steering committee.','Detective','Semi-automated','SOC 2 CC4.1','Monthly'),
('Process Safety Performance Indicator (PSPI) Monitoring','Tracks leading and lagging process safety KPIs including near misses, barrier health, and inspection overdue rates. Escalated to board level.','Detective','Semi-automated','API RP 754 | IOGP 456 | ISO 45001','Monthly'),
('Environmental Compliance Monitoring','Monitors environmental performance indicators (emissions, effluent, waste) against permit limits and internal targets. Breaches escalated and reported.','Detective','Semi-automated','ISO 14001 | Local environmental regulations','Continuous'),
('OT Security Monitoring and Anomaly Detection','Monitors OT/SCADA network traffic for anomalous commands, unusual device behaviour, and known attack patterns specific to industrial control systems.','Detective','Automated','IEC 62443 | NIST SP 800-82','Continuous'),
('Inventory and Stock Count Audit','Regular cycle counts and annual full stock counts to detect shrinkage, administrative errors, and supplier short-shipment. Reconciled to stock records.','Detective','Manual','SOC 2 CC5.2','Monthly cycle count; annual full count'),
('Trade Finance Document Verification','Independent review of trade documents (bills of lading, certificates of origin, inspection reports) before payment release. Detects fraud and discrepancies.','Detective','Manual','UCP 600 | Local banking regulations','Per transaction'),
('Sharia Audit','Annual independent audit by qualified Sharia auditors to verify that products, processes, and transactions comply with approved Sharia standards and SSB fatwas.','Detective','Manual','AAOIFI | Local Central Bank Islamic finance regulations','Annual'),
('Aviation Safety Reporting System','Confidential reporting system for crew and staff to report safety events, near misses, and hazards without fear of punitive action. Data analysed for trends.','Detective','Semi-automated','ICAO Annex 13 | GCAA SMS requirements | IOSA','Continuous'),
('Incident Response Plan','Documented plan covering identification, containment, eradication, recovery, and lessons learned for security incidents. Roles clearly assigned.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.16 | SOC 2 CC7.3 | NIST IR-4','Annual test'),
('Data Breach Notification Procedure','Documented procedure for notifying regulators and affected individuals within required timeframes following a confirmed data breach.','Corrective','Manual','GDPR Art.33-34 | PDPL | SOC 2 CC7.4','Per incident'),
('Disaster Recovery Procedure','Step-by-step recovery playbooks for critical systems. Tested against RTO/RPO targets. Includes escalation contacts and decision authorities.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 A1.3 | NIST CP-10','Annual test'),
('Crisis Management and Communications Plan','Defines the Crisis Management Team, activation criteria, decision-making process, and communications strategy for major incidents.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 CC7.4','Annual exercise'),
('Root Cause Analysis Process','Structured methodology for investigating significant incidents to identify root causes and prevent recurrence. Findings tracked to closure.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.16.1.6 | SOC 2 CC7.4 | NIST IR-5','Per significant incident'),
('Account Suspension and Access Revocation','Immediate suspension of user accounts on detection of compromise or policy violation. Automated where possible; manual fallback.','Corrective','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.9.2.6 | SOC 2 CC6.2 | NIST AC-2(3)','Per event'),
('Emergency Patch Deployment','Accelerated patching for critical zero-day or actively exploited vulnerabilities. Bypasses normal change cycle with appropriate authorisation.','Corrective','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.12.6.1 | SOC 2 CC7.1 | NIST SI-2','Per event'),
('BCP Activation','Process for activating BCP in response to a disruption event. Clear trigger criteria; CMT convenes; recovery procedures enacted.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 A1.3','Per event'),
('Disciplinary and Performance Management','Formal process for addressing employee misconduct or performance issues. Consistent, documented, and compliant with employment law.','Corrective','Manual','SOC 2 CC1.1 | ISO 27001 A.7.2.3','Per event'),
('Supplier Remediation and Replacement','Process for placing failing suppliers on improvement plans. Activates contingency suppliers when primary cannot remediate.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.15.2 | SOC 2 CC9.2','Per event'),
('Customer Complaint Resolution','Structured process for acknowledging, investigating, and resolving client complaints. Tracks resolution time and recurring issues.','Corrective','Manual','SOC 2 CC2.3','Per event'),
('Legal and Regulatory Escalation','Process for escalating potential legal or regulatory breaches to legal counsel and regulators. Includes self-reporting where required.','Corrective','Manual','SOC 2 CC4.2 | ISO 27001 A.18.1','Per event'),
('Insurance Claims Management','Process for notifying insurers and managing claims promptly following a covered loss.','Corrective','Manual','SOC 2 A1.1','Per event'),
('Malware Quarantine and Remediation','Automated quarantine of infected files and systems on detection. Remediation playbook covering eradication, restoration, and verification.','Corrective','Semi-automated','ISO 27001 A.12.2 | SOC 2 CC7.3 | NIST IR-4','Per event'),
('HR Grievance Process','Formal process for employees to raise workplace grievances. Ensures fair, timely investigation and resolution.','Corrective','Manual','SOC 2 CC1.1','Per event'),
('Evidence Preservation Procedure','Process for preserving digital and physical evidence following an incident to support investigation and potential legal proceedings.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 27001 A.16.1 | SOC 2 CC7.3 | NIST IR-4','Per event'),
('Environmental Spill Response Plan','Documented plan for immediate containment, notification, and remediation of environmental spills or releases. Pre-positioned equipment and trained response teams.','Corrective','Manual','ISO 14001 | Local environmental emergency regulations','Per event'),
('Process Safety Incident Investigation','Structured investigation of process safety incidents and near misses using recognised methodologies (bow-tie, ICAM). Findings shared across organisation and industry where appropriate.','Corrective','Manual','API RP 585 | IOGP | ISO 45001','Per significant event'),
('Product Recall Procedure','Documented procedure for rapid withdrawal of unsafe products from supply chain and customers. Includes regulator notification, customer communication, and media response.','Corrective','Manual','Local food authority / product safety regulations','Per event'),
('Information Security Policy','Top-level policy establishing the organisation''s commitment to information security, scope, principles, and accountability. Board-approved.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.5.1.1 | SOC 2 CC1.3','Annual review'),
('Data Protection and Privacy Policy','Defines how personal data is collected, used, stored, and shared in compliance with applicable privacy laws (GDPR, PDPL, etc.).','Directive','Manual','GDPR Art.24 | UAE PDPL | ISO 27701 | SOC 2 P1','Annual review'),
('Code of Conduct and Ethics Policy','Establishes expected standards of behaviour for all employees and contractors: integrity, conflict of interest, gifts, anti-bribery.','Directive','Manual','SOC 2 CC1.3 | ISO 37001','Annual review'),
('Business Continuity Policy','Defines the organisation''s commitment to continuity, sets RTO/RPO targets, assigns BCM ownership, and mandates annual testing.','Directive','Manual','ISO 22301 | SOC 2 A1.2','Annual review'),
('IT Change Management Policy','Governs how changes to systems, processes, and infrastructure are proposed, assessed, approved, implemented, and reviewed.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.12.1.2 | SOC 2 CC8.1','Annual review'),
('Supplier / Third-Party Management Policy','Defines requirements for supplier selection, risk assessment, contracting, ongoing monitoring, and exit.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.15 | SOC 2 CC9.2','Annual review'),
('Whistleblower / Speak-Up Policy','Guarantees non-retaliation for good-faith reports. Defines reporting channels and investigation process.','Directive','Manual','SOC 2 CC1.5 | ISO 37001','Annual review'),
('Incident Response Policy','Defines how the organisation responds to security incidents: roles, responsibilities, escalation, notification, and post-incident review.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.16 | SOC 2 CC7.3','Annual review'),
('Access Management Policy','Sets minimum requirements for password complexity, MFA, access provisioning, access reviews, and privileged access management.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.9 | SOC 2 CC6.1-6.3','Annual review'),
('Remote Working and BYOD Policy','Defines security requirements for remote work and personal devices. Covers VPN, encryption, and physical security.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.6.2.2 | SOC 2 CC6.1','Annual review'),
('Risk Management Policy','Establishes the approach to identifying, assessing, treating, and monitoring risks. Defines risk appetite and tolerance.','Directive','Manual','ISO 31000 | SOC 2 CC3.1','Annual review'),
('Backup and Recovery Policy','Defines backup frequency, retention periods, storage requirements, encryption standards, and restore testing obligations.','Directive','Manual','ISO 27001 A.12.3 | SOC 2 A1.2 | NIST CP-9','Annual review'),
('Health, Safety and Environment (HSE) Policy','Board-level commitment to protecting people and the environment. Sets HSE objectives, assigns accountability, and mandates the management system.','Directive','Manual','ISO 45001 | ISO 14001 | Local HSE regulations','Annual review'),
('Process Safety Management Standard','Defines requirements for managing major accident hazards in process industries: PHA, PTW, MOC, mechanical integrity, emergency response, and incident investigation.','Directive','Manual','OSHA PSM | API RP 750 | SEVESO III | Local HSEQ regulations','Annual review'),
('Sharia Compliance Policy','Board-approved policy committing the organisation to Sharia compliance. Defines the role of the SSB, approval process, and prohibition of non-compliant structures.','Directive','Manual','AAOIFI | IFSB | Local Central Bank Islamic finance regulations','Annual review'),
('Trade Compliance and Sanctions Policy','Defines the organisation''s obligations regarding trade sanctions, export controls, and AML in trade finance. Assigns compliance officer accountability.','Directive','Manual','OFAC | EU Dual-use Regulation | UN Security Council Resolutions | Local regulations','Annual review');
